      "title": "VPN Troubleshooting Guide",
      "content": "Step 1: Check VPN tunnel status using 'show crypto isakmp sa'. Step 2: Verify Phase 1 and Phase 2 status. Step 3: Check firewall rules allowing VPN traffic. Step 4: Verify routing to remote subnet.",
