      "answer": "Check bandwidth usage in PRTG. If usage is high, check for unusual traffic. If low, reboot router.",
      "category": "Network"
    },
    {
      "id": "FAQ-002",
      "question": "POS machine not connecting",
      "answer": "Check network cable. Verify POS IP address. Check firewall rule allowing POS traffic.",
